<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.5">
<l>viṭuvē ṉōveṉ viḷakkaiyeṉ ṉāviyai</l>
<l>naṭuvē vantuyyak koḷkiṉṟa nātaṉait</l>
<l>toṭuvē ceytiḷa vāycciyark kaṇṇiṉuḷ</l>
<l>viṭavē ceytu viḻikkum pirāṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I let go of my light, my soul,</l>
<l>the leader who came in the middle [and] managed to escape(?),</l>
<l>the lord who opened the eyes, committing theft,</l> 
<l>committing licentiousness among the young cowherder women?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
